entries.title_d: The Coynite have apparently been defeated and it is time to return to standard duties. A prison ship is preparing a drop on Dathomir and needs an escort through the system. Meet and escort this prison ship.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Escort the Prison Shuttle
entries.thanks_5: I still can't believe that there are more of those mercs out there.

entries.taunt_5: You are a fool to think you could beat us so easily.
entries.taunt_4: Draw your last breath and prepare to die!
entries.taunt_3: Your heart shall not beat another day.
entries.taunt_2: You are the one who destroyed Coyn's Tempest. Time to pay the price!
entries.split_quest_alert: It appears that the Coynite were not defeated as we had hoped. This appears to have been a decoy attack for their real plan to get a ship off of the planet's surface. Stand by for more information.
entries.shields_depleted: There went our shields. Get those fighters off of us.
entries.reason_5: I have a ship full of enemies of the state that need to be dropped to the prison. Should be a smooth ride.

entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Travel to the navigation waypoint and wait for the arrival of the prison ship.
entries.quest_location_d: The prison ship will meet you in the Dathomir system.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort and protect the prison ship until it makes its prison drop.
entries.panic_5: Coynite mercenaries! Didn't you kill all of them?
entries.panic_4: What! I thought these mercs were driven out of this sector?
entries.panic_3: Coynite mercenaries! Didn't you kill all of them?
entries.panic_2: The mercs are back! I don't think that was their command vessel.
entries.panic_1: What! I thought these mercs were driven out of this sector?
entries.hull_half: \#FF0000 Our hull is down to half strength! We are not going to last much longer.
entries.goodbye_5: Thanks for the escort. You had better find out why those Coynites are still in the sector though.

entries.found_loc: The prison transport will arrive at this nav location. Meet that ship here and escort it through the sector.
entries.failed_protect: You left your target. This is unacceptable. Report back to command.
entries.failed_destroy: They were only prisoners but that is no excuse for failing a direct order. Report back to your superior.
entries.complete: Prison ship depositing it's cargo on the planet surface. Nice work, pilot.
entries.arrived_at_loc: Stand by for arrival of Prison transport. We anticipate a smooth flight.
entries.abort: Your orders were to escort us through this area. High Command will hear of this failure I assure you.
